import api from'./api';export const clientService={// Get all clients
getAllClients:()=>api.get('/clients'),// Get client by ID
getClientById:id=>api.get("/clients/".concat(id)),// Create new client
createClient:clientData=>api.post('/clients',clientData),// Update client
updateClient:(id,clientData)=>api.put("/clients/".concat(id),clientData),// Delete client
deleteClient:id=>api.delete("/clients/".concat(id)),// Search clients
searchClients:query=>api.get("/clients/search?query=".concat(encodeURIComponent(query))),// Get clients by collector
getClientsByCollector:collectorId=>api.get("/clients/collector/".concat(collectorId))};
